00:14:24.260 --> 00:14:25.860
Cuide dele.

00:14:26.600 --> 00:14:27.140
Entendido.

00:14:33.480 --> 00:14:34.640
Vamos continuar!

00:14:35.070 --> 00:14:35.560
Sim!

00:14:41.160 --> 00:14:42.930
Luminus Ball

00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:49.760
Eternity Reflexion

